2016;;Joe Cinque's Consolation;;Australian;;Sotiris Dounoukos;;Maggie Naouri, Jerome Meyer;;drama, true crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Cinque%27s_Consolation_(film);;Anu Singh, an Australian National University student, drugged her boyfriend Joe Cinque's coffee with Rohypnol and injected him with heroin in 1997. The other guests of the dinner party in which this incident took place were aware of the murder plot and yet nobody warned him.